&lt;p&gt;I think that’s it for quick update of my side project. If you’re reading it until the end of the page, let’s connect on &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/afnizarnur&quot;&gt;Twitter&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[Personal Website Refresh]]></title><description><![CDATA[It's time to launch my personal website, again and it's always a work in progress.]]></description><link>https://afnizarnur.com/2020/writing/personal-website-refresh-2020/</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://afnizarnur.com/2020/writing/personal-website-refresh-2020/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2020 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;In this post, I will tell you some of the things behind the personal website refresh. But most of the reason is about &lt;a href=&quot;https://afnizarnur.com/writing/giving-back-to-community/&quot;&gt;giving back to community&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
